    "description": "<strong>你是伟大的古代俄罗斯骑士</strong>, 在蜥蜴的巢穴中卧底. <strong>为您的斯拉夫兄弟获取智慧</strong>, <strong>将古代俄罗斯手稿归还基地</strong>, <strong>取贝加尔水并摧毁蜥蜴基地</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0b5aa7b43a5729f3f80cb6e4faffeed9.avif?t=1725325521\" width=587 height=247 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的特征</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>收集5个斯拉夫手稿</strong><br></li><li><strong>喝18罐贝加尔水</strong><br></li><li><strong>您可以进入4个主要和2个奖励位置 - 销毁所有蜥蜴基地</strong><br></li><li><strong>15种蜥蜴</strong><br></li><li><strong>三个伟大的俄罗斯骑士</strong> - 选择你的英雄<br></li><li><strong>飞行的恐龙将带您到蜥蜴的巢穴</strong><br></li><li><strong>斯拉夫人与恐龙结盟</strong>, 所以古老的俄罗斯人有 <strong>翼手龙，霸王龙和三角龙可以使用</strong><br></li><li><strong>古代俄罗斯太空飞船是根据蜥蜴偷来的技术组装的</strong><br></li><li><strong>斯拉夫伟大的气氛和声音效果</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/6dd2055c919b9e95660c49926fa3533a.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/6dd2055c919b9e95660c49926fa3533a.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/6dd2055c919b9e95660c49926fa3533a.mp4?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重要功能</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>在物体（岩石，天王星，树木，冰等）上紧缩以恢复骑士健康</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/052e37c2278f9f593f9477f9481bf7c0.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=247 height=291 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/052e37c2278f9f593f9477f9481bf7c0.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要位置</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>蜥蜴营</strong> - 在古老的Rus Capital的墙壁下的森林里有一个蜥蜴营地<br></li><li><strong>贝加尔湖</strong> - 伟大的战斗发生在这里，但现在这个地方在蜥蜴的力量之下，帮助斯拉夫人将贝加尔返回原生港口<br></li><li><strong>火星 </strong>- 转移到火星的蜥蜴军事基地<br></li><li><strong>nibiru </strong>- 探索家乡星球和主要蜥蜴避风港</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/52de6a2044f20324ab885517dfd791c6.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/52de6a2044f20324ab885517dfd791c6.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/52de6a2044f20324ab885517dfd791c6.mp4?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >奖励位置</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>圣彼得堡</strong> - 蜥蜴占领了这座城市，走在城市的主要街道上，追捕每个蜥蜴<br></li><li><strong>元旦的冬季森林</strong> - 通过从俄罗斯大森林中追逐蜥蜴来庆祝新年</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0eefee70d1ced7c388fc13b02c352f5c.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0eefee70d1ced7c388fc13b02c352f5c.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0eefee70d1ced7c388fc13b02c352f5c.mp4?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
